---
title: Cal Smart Gochujang Turkey Bowls with Pickled Radishes
description: These bowls brim with sautéed turkey and veggies coated in a sweet gochujang sauce. Warming spice from the poblanos provides a delicious contrast. It's all heaped on top of fragrant sesame rice with bright DIY pickled radishes adding the final flourish.
